Package net.grinder.console.model

The console model.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
SampleListener Listener interface for sample statistics notifications.
SampleModel Interface to SampleModelImplementation.
SampleModel.Listener Interface for listeners to SampleModelImplementation.
SampleModel.State A snapshot of the model state.
SampleModelViews Statistics views to use with the statistics from the SampleModel.
SampleModelViews.Listener Interface for listeners.
 

Class Summary
ConsoleProperties Class encapsulating the console options.
ConsolePropertyDefaults Console property default value constants.
ModelTestIndex Immutable snapshot of current test structure that is valid at time of notification.
SampleAccumulator Manages the cumulative statistics for a single test or set of tests.
SampleModel.AbstractListener Skeleton implementation of SampleModel.Listener.
SampleModelImplementation Collate test reports into samples and distribute to listeners.
SampleModelViewsImplementation Statistics views to use with the statistics from the Sample SampleModel.
